：<br />\n<br />\n-血跡拖住地下痕跡（1.冇救護員冇擔架 2.死者太重要拖行）<br />\n-某部份地下特別乾淨（謀殺案想毁屍滅跡）"},{"pid":"b0a8e8485c159e5cdc0339b2364ac6c4eac675fc","tid":1546691,"uid":152815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7835421d9e14408c9aecd58869407334f2a27bc","tid":1546691,"uid":123408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}